      "span_text": "The International Vitreomacular Traction Study (IVTS) group has developed an OCT-based classification of the vitreomacular interface.  In this classification, vitreomacular adhesion (VMA) is defined as perifoveal vitreous separation with remaining vitreomacular attachment and unperturbated foveal morphologic features."
